            'Ollama maintains a curated model library (ollama.com/library) with one-command downloads for Meta Llama 3.1, Microsoft Phi-3, Google Gemma 2, Mistral 7B, Qwen2.5, and 100+ other models. A model is downloaded once and cached on disk вҖ” subsequent runs start in under 5 seconds.',
            'For alternatives to Ollama, see [Local LLM One-Click Installers](/local-llms/local-llm-one-click-installers). To compare Ollama with LM Studio, see [How to Install LM Studio](/local-llms/how-to-install-lm-studio).',
