            '**Ollama is the best choice for developers who want a REST API and terminal-first workflow.** Ollama runs as a background service and exposes an OpenAI-compatible REST API at `http://localhost:11434`. It has no graphical interface of its own вҖ” you interact with it through the terminal or via third-party UIs like [Open WebUI](/local-llms/desktop-vs-webui-local-llm?lang=en).',
            'Ollama maintains a curated model library at ollama.com/library with approximately 200 models. Each model is pulled with a single command: `ollama pull llama3.1:8b`. Models are stored in `~/.ollama/models`.',
