            'A 7B model at FP16 = ~14 GB RAM. At Q4_K_M = ~4.5 GB. At Q8_0 = ~7 GB.',
            'Quality loss at Q4_K_M is 1вҖ“3% on MMLU benchmarks compared to FP16 вҖ” imperceptible in most practical tasks.',
