      title: 'Long Context Local LLMs: Which Models Handle 32K, 128K Tokens Locally?',
      seoTitle: 'Long Context Local LLMs 2026',
      intro: 'Most local LLM models in 2026 support 128K token context windows on paper, but practical usable context вҖ” where quality stays high вҖ” is typically 16KвҖ“32K tokens. Llama 3.1/3.2/3.3, Qwen2.5, and Mistral Small 3.1 all support 128K context. Processing full-length documents or books locally requires understanding RAM scaling and quality degradation at long ranges.',
      metaDescription: 'Long context local LLMs: which models support 32K, 128K tokens locally, RAM requirements for long contexts, and practical limits before. Free beta вҖ” April 2026.',
