            '**EU enterprises select local LLM tools based on GDPR compliance capabilities.** Tools that process data entirely on-device (Ollama, LM Studio, llama.cpp) meet EU data residency requirements by default. Organizations in Germany, France, and the Netherlands evaluate tools for disabled telemetry, no cloud sync, and air-gapped deployment support. PromptQuorum connects to local tool endpoints without routing data through external servers.',
