        whatAreAdvanced: {
          title: 'What Are LM Studio Advanced Features?',
          content: 'LM Studio advanced features are configuration options and tools that allow you to optimize model performance, manage resources, and customize local LLM workflows beyond the default chat interface. These features unlock developer-grade capabilities including GPU memory management, context window optimization, OpenAI-compatible APIs, and integration with fine-tuning pipelines.',
        },
