            '**Optimize memory usage** вҖ” Control VRAM allocation per model, extend or restrict context length, and manage system resources for multi-tasking.',
            '**Create production APIs** вҖ” Expose local models via OpenAI-compatible REST endpoints for seamless integration with existing applications.',
