      theme: 'Privacy & Business',
      title: 'Local LLM Setup for Business Teams',
      seoTitle: 'Multi-User Local LLM for Teams: Setup, Access Control, Cost Analysis',
      intro: '**Deploy a shared local LLM server for 5вҖ“20 team members using vLLM + nginx load balancer.** As of April 2026, team-scale inference costs $50/month (electricity) vs. $1,000+/month (cloud APIs). This guide covers multi-user access, role-based permissions, usage metering, and cost attribution.',
